The following article is a part of the [http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/and-every-time-we-meet-again-hub And Every Time We Meet Again] storyline. Whilst you can read it on its own, it's highly recommended you read the previous installments to get this article in its fullest.

**Image Sources:**

The Site-120 logo used in the header was created by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]] for the purpose of all articles regarding such. Please check out more of their absolutely stellar work [[[Desk of Junior Designer S. Yvonne|here]]].

