[[div class="blockquote"]]

**From:** ##c90000|@@m.cornwell@site.120.int@@##
**To:** ##c90000|O5-9##
**Subject:** SCP-5672 1985 Activation Event Report Log
**Date:** 23/05/1985
-----
Miss,

As requested, I'm sending over SCP-5672's Activation Event Report Log taken directly from Dr. Asheworth's body camera following the acquiring of his clothing by my brother, during his mission "to finally end [[[and-every-time-we-meet-again-hub|the case]]]," as he put it. Additionally, the body you requested should arrive within your office within two days' time.

Please see attached file for the full log.

I wish I had known him more. Maybe then we could have understood before it was too late. I am truly sorry I hadn't done more to help.

[[>]]
Sincerely,
-- Magdaleine Cornwell
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

